**Cop** | Townsfolk Investigative
__Basics__
The **cop** may check one player per night to see if they are a member of the mafia. They will see a player as either "mafia" or "not mafia".

__Formalized__
End Night: [Quantity: %Number%]
  • Process: Alignment Investigate @Selection (SD)
  • Evaluate:
    ‣ @Result is `Mafia`[alignment]: `Mafia`
    ‣ Otherwise: `Not Mafia`
